<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink399" corresp="#TNV23poem28">
<l>nummaṉaic cilampu kaḻīi yayariṉu</l>
<l>memmaṉai vatuvai naṉmaṇaṅ kaḻikeṉac</l>
<l>colli ṉevaṉō maṟṟē veṉvēṉ</l>
<l>maiyaṟa viḷaṅkiya kaḻalaṭip</l>
<l>poyval kāḷaiyai yīṉṟa tāykkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l> What if [you] tell the mother who gave birth to that young man, </l>
<l> master of lies, his spear victorious,</l>
<l> his feet in gleaming faultless anklets: </l>
<l> “Although in your house [her] anklet was taken off,</l>
<l> let us perform a good marriage [ceremony] in our house!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
